Analytics for Communications - Consumer Dashboards
Account Highlights
Subscription Highlights
The Account Highlights embedded dashboard surfaces key account-level metrics such as customer tenure, customer lifetime value, total interactions, average handling time, data usage, total spend, and payment frequency.
If there’s at least 120 days of historical data, you see a comparison of the last 30 and 90 days of usage, payment, and payment frequency data.

The Subscription Highlights embedded dashboard surfaces key subscription-level metrics such as customer interactions, average handling time, data usage, total spend, and days since last payment.
When the payment and usage data isn’t available for the account or subscription, the dashboard shows first call resolution, activation time, and orders instead of the payment and usage metrics.
